interactive user input interfaces. tells the user what files are too big, suggests tags, etc

making post:
	show user:
		who they are posting as
		what fields they still need to fill
	
	
broadcasting system:
	each ui element anounces when an event has occured on it or data being represented has changed
	
user panel:
	it has different states: no user logged in, user logged in, user trying to register (enter password again and email), user registered (show make bio box)

